Since Stephanie went to prom with Michael's son, this makes Stephanie a graduate and Michael a dad.
Since Elias and James played on the high school team, this makes Stephanie, Elias, and James the three graduates.
By process of elimination, this makes Alberto, Ken, and Michael the three dads.
Michael and Elias are not related, which makes Michael's sont to be James.
Because Alberto's son played on the high school team, this makes Elias to be Alberto's son.
By process of elimination, Ken is Stephanie's dad.

Alberto -> Elias
Ken -> Stephanie
Michael -> James
